## 3. Implementing Your Service

The scaffold registers `I{{ model.names.dot_net_class_name }}` as a placeholder that throws `NotImplementedException`. Your first task is to implement it.

### Step 1 — Create the implementation

Create `Services/{{ model.names.dot_net_class_name }}Impl.cs`:

```csharp
/*
