### Caching

```csharp
// Cache a response (5 minutes)
await _cache.SetAsync("{{ model.names.cache_prefix }}{id}", response, TimeSpan.FromMinutes(5), ct);

// Read from cache
var cached = await _cache.GetAsync<{{ model.names.dot_net_class_name }}Response>("{{ model.names.cache_prefix }}{id}", ct);

// Invalidate on mutation
await _cache.RemoveAsync("{{ model.names.cache_prefix }}{id}", ct);
```

